this is a java graphic engin(no audio code now)

run print exception about -Djava.library.path  please add the native library support . same that
toolbar->Run->Run Configurations...->java Application->Arguements->VM arguements 
-Djava.library.path="F:\.m2\repository\org\lwjgl\lwjgl\lwjgl-platform\2.9.3\lwjgl-platform-2.9.3-natives-windows"

my platform library path as the "F:\.m2\repository\org\lwjgl\lwjgl\lwjgl-platform\2.9.3\lwjgl-platform-2.9.3-natives-windows"

启动的时候会报错是因为没有指定本地依赖的动态库
在虚拟机运行配置选项里面的 加上
-Djava.library.path="F:\.m2\repository\org\lwjgl\lwjgl\lwjgl-platform\2.9.3\lwjgl-platform-2.9.3-natives-windows"

// vertex shader decide the 1.vertex positions 2.decide 

//fragment shader decide the per pixel color 

// cartoon shader
void mian(void){
	vec4 textureColor = texture(texture_diffuse,pass_TextureCoord);
	
	if(matCount>1.5){
		if(textureColor.a>0.75){
		
		}else if(textureColor.a>0.5){
			textureColor = textureColor*vec4(colorMat1,1.0);
		}else if(textureColor.a>0.25){
			textureColor = textureColor*vec4(colorMat2,1.0);
		}
	}else if(matCount>0.5){
		if(textureColor.a>0.75){
		
		}else if(textureColor.a>0.5){
			textureColor = textureColor*vec4(colorMat1,1.0);
		}
	}
	
	if(blendingOn<0.5&& textureColor.a<0.5){
		discard;
	}
}
